<h2 id="lab-visits">Lab Visits</h2>

<h3 id="tuesday">Tuesday</h3>

<p><em>Human-Robot Fist Bump Human &amp; Intention Tracking for Collaborative Assembly</em></p>

<p>Demo by Ye-Ji Mun from Prof. Katie Driggs-Campbell‚Äôs Group</p>

<p>Illinois Robotics Lab</p>

<ol>
  <li>Human-Robot Fist Bump: The Kinova retrieves a human‚Äôs fist pose from its mounted camera and follows the human‚Äôs fist movement using visual servoing technique.</li>
  <li>Human Intention Tracking for Collaborative Assembly: A human worker and a UR5e robot work together to assemble industrial connectors. After the human aligns the connector parts, the UR5e pushes the aligned connectors for their insertion.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="wednesday">Wednesday</h3>

<p><em>RTAB-Map &amp; Image Goal Navigation</em></p>

<p>Demo by Justin Wasserman from Prof. Girish Chowdhary‚Äôs Group</p>

<p>ECEB 5072</p>

